{"tid":1509781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文戰庫務及物流署。","createTime":"2019-08-27T03:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T03:22:40.000Z","uid":275595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c3e7ced6980aea25c13df82a3cebd6d5ad8b36","tid":1509781,"uid":275595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"轉載<br />\n<br />\n我朋友响政府做。佢唔方便出真身。<br />\n<br />\n佢建議大家同時都用文戰搞庫務局或物流署。<br />\n<br />\n而且建議成立控告基金，用民事訴訟去告警察，等佢哋內鬨，讓警察互相篤灰。<br />\n<br />\n超過五百萬嘅購買，一定要落tender，要出憲，例如要買催淚彈都會超過五百萬。政府內部用錢，要經庫務，其他物資用物流署。佢話多咗好多警察响警總過夜，所以厠紙都用多咗。<br />\n<br />\n另外，佢話破壞警總立會嗰啲，警察唔痛唔癢，因為會搵亞姐清潔，建築署油油，搵機電工程署連返啲電綫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>我都曾經諗過會唔會眾籌 懸紅， 等警察自己舉報黑警及721。"},{"pid":"de059e805627195c46722dd07f350aad07abc03d","tid":1509781,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=fc9e2e27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=959e7b8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=629e964e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"34fc8e7fc538cfa5c541066e0853173d50aaad4a","tid":1509781,"uid":41829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:15:44.000Z","msg":"說服警犬前線一齊罷工，要佢地明白，佢地幫高層執屎，高層就同黑社會茶煙飽炮"},{"pid":"8fcd4fe0853e0a017d39b0bb5833664bdd3945f1","tid":1509781,"uid":275595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:22:40.000Z","msg":"我都曾經諗過會唔會眾籌 懸紅， 等警察自己舉報黑警及721。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無人敵得過錢， 佢哋會疑神疑鬼剋制自己 ，當有人出黎舉報，政府亦無得再死撐黑警。<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手諗諗，咁被人拉唔係辦法。"}]}